    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A spring-loaded ankle and calf, which are also fitted with shock absorbers.</p><p>If installed in one leg, reduce the movement penalty while jumping horizontally by half. Additionally, reduce any damage taken from falls by half if the user lands on their feet, and the DV of the athletics check required to avoid the Broken Leg critical injury is reduced by 2.</p><p>If paired, the user negates the movement penalty for jumping (horizontally) and can jump 2x their height vertically (a normal character will typically be around 1.6-1.9m tall). Additionally he distance before the user begins taking damage from falls/must roll to avoid the Broken Leg critical injury is increased to 30m/yds.</p>"
